snippet.title: Upside Town - Walkabout Mini Golf - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It's finally time to take a swing at the most topsy turvy mini golf course the world has never known! Here in Upside Town, it is always a weirdly beautiful day—where gravity fields permeate the streets, walkways, walls, facades, rooftops, and ceilings. NOW OPEN FOR BUSINESS!

Available on @MetaQuestVR and SteamVR!
